{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ce4dbd20-acda-4abc-b4f5-00f6abe11597","content":"There are no workflow files in this directory. Since I can't review your specific workflow, here's a general guide for switching from `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` to **NuGet trusted publishing (OIDC)**:\n\n### 1. NuGet.org setup\n- Go to **NuGet.org → Manage Packages → Trusted Publishers**\n- Add a new **GitHub Actions** publisher policy, specifying your repo, branch/tag, and optionally the workflow file and environment name.\n\n### 2. Workflow changes\n\n**Add OIDC permissions** to your job:\n```yaml\npermissions:\n  id-token: write   # Required for OIDC token\n  contents: read\n```\n\n**Replace** your `dotnet nuget push` step:\n```yaml\n# BEFORE (API key)\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }} --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n\n# AFTER (trusted publishing)\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n  env:\n    NUGET_TOKEN: \"\"  # not needed; OIDC handles auth\n```\n\nActually, the exact mechanism depends on tooling support. The current recommended approach:\n\n```yaml\n- name: Push to NuGet\n  run: |\n    dotnet nuget add source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json \\\n      --name nuget.org \\\n      --username \"az\" \\\n      --password \"${{ steps.oidc.outputs.id-token }}\" \\\n      --store-password-in-clear-text\n    dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg --source nuget.org\n```\n\n### 3. Remove the secret\nOnce verified, delete `NUGET_API_KEY` from your repo's **Settings → Secrets**.\n\n### Key points\n- **`id-token: write`** permission is mandatory\n- The trusted publisher policy on NuGet.org must match your repo/branch/environment exactly\n- Consider using a GitHub **environment** with protection rules for extra security\n- Test with a pre-release package first\n\nWould you like me to help modify a specific workflow file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"c81bfae2-0f95-4031-b580-072f68da1443","outputTokens":536,"requestId":"4BCA:20A2EF:5DC2A69:69029E9:69EC0EEB"},"id":"56fcd964-71af-4a49-b428-1b02baea6ba9","timestamp":"2026-04-25T00:46:47.689Z","parentId":"1d96270d-aaaa-420f-ad78-f75082ad89f1"}
